ary/crime/serial_killers/notorious/dahmer/8.html |archivedate=August 31, 2009}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Bardsley-10\">{{cite web |url=http://www.trutv.com/library/crime/serial_killers/notorious/dahmer/10.html |title=Jeffrey Dahmer&nbsp;\u2013 Serial Killer and Cannibal&nbsp;\u2013 The Killing Binge |last=Bardsley |first=Marilyn |work=TruTV.com |publisher=TruTV Crime Library |accessdate=July 26, 2010 |url-status=unfit |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019120548/https://www.trutv.com/library/crime/serial_killers/notorious/dahmer/10.html |archivedate=October 10, 2013}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Bardsley-21\">{{cite web|url=http://www.trutv.com/library/crime/serial_killers/notorious/dahmer/21.html |title=Jeffrey Dahmer&nbsp;\u2013 Serial Killer and Cannibal&nbsp;\u2013 End of the Road |last=Bardsley |first=Marilyn |work=TruTV.com |publisher=TruTV Crime Library |accessdate=July 26, 2010 |url-status=unfit |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110519084408/http://www.trutv.com/library/crime/serial_killers/notorious/dahmer/21.html |archivedate=May 19, 2011}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Bardsley-22\">{{cite web|url=http://www.trutv.com/library/crime/serial_killers/notorious/dahmer/22.html |title=Jeffrey Dahmer&nbsp;\u2013 Serial Killer and Cannibal&nbsp;\u2013 Did Dahmer Find God? |last=Bardsley |first=Marilyn |work=TruTV.com |publisher=TruTV Crime Library |accessdate=July 26, 2010 |url-status=unfit |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090904192409/http://www.trutv.com/library/crime/serial_killers/notorious/dahmer/22.html |archivedate=September 4, 2009}}</ref>\n}}\n\n==Cited works==\n*{{cite book |last= Aggrawal |first= Anil |title=Necrophilia: Forensic and Medico-legal Aspects|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=b0k2qpfyU8IC|year= 2016 |publisher=[[CRC Press]]|location=Boca Raton, Florida|isbn=978-1-4200-8913-4|ref=harv}}\n*{{cite book |editor-last=Campbell|editor-first=Duncan|title=Murder in Mind&nbsp;\u2013 Jeffrey Dahmer the Milwaukee serial killer|publisher=[[Marshall 